The paper deals with 3D computer vision, computer graphics, and robotics, which are all related to computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The paper also introduces a new learning-based approach for shape representation, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the potential applications of the proposed method in robotics, which falls under robotics (cs.RO).
